Package com.sponsorpay.publisher.interstitial

Interface Summary
SPInterstitialAdListener Interface that defines the methods to be implemented in order to get notifications about the status of an ad.
SPInterstitialRequestListener Interface to be implemented by listeners notified of the results of an Interstitial request.
 

Class Summary
SPInterstitialActivity Activity that is responsible for showing an interstitial ad
SPInterstitialAd Class holding the information about a specific Intersitial Ad.
SPInterstitialAdsProcessor Internal class processing the back-end response for interstitial ads.
SPInterstitialClient Provides methods to request and show Interstitial Ads and notifies its listener SPInterstitialAdListener of the ad status result.
SPInterstitialEventDispatcher Internal class dispatches the intersitital events.
SPInterstitialRequester Internal class that will perform a back-end query for interstitial ads.
 

Enum Summary
SPInterstitialAdCloseReason Represents the reason why an interstitial ad was dismissed.
SPInterstitialClientState The Interstitial client internal state
SPInterstitialEvent Intersitial tracking events
